Pandaboard FPGA and data-acquisition expansion:  Hardware and FPGA sources
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

hardware/  gEDA design files (gschem and pcb)
  |
  | gschem-sym/    gschem symbols and pin assignments
  | pcb-elements/  pcb footprints

fpga/      Spartan-6 FPGA sources
  |
  | modules/       HDL for FPGA modules 
  | synth/         Bitstream build support 
                   (requires Xilinx ISE Webpack install) 

tools/     Miscellaneous tools

